Syntactically Awesome StyleSheets
  Sass and Scss

Variables
    $variableName: value;
    $d: Helvetica, sans-serif;
    $e: 1px #000 solid 0 0;
  Operations
    font-size: 4px + 4;
  Color Functions
    lighten($color, 10%);
    darken($color, 10%);
  String Interpolation
    "#{$root}background.jpg"
Using Variables
  $mainColor: Black;
